                h2.caps The Build
                p After multiple rounds of user testing and prototype iteration are complete, creative and technical development begin. Adhering to our mantra--Build Small, Learn Fast, Iterate Often--we first develop a Minimum Viable Product, or MVP
        .row.process-row
            .col-xs-12.col-md-6
                h5.caps MVP
                p A Minimum Viable Product (MVP) is the first iteration of a product that fulfills the product purpose and objectives defined and validated during the preflight. MVP product development creates user validated digital products, often in shorter timelines and at lower costs. When the core product is valuable, users will actually help guide the additional feature priorities during future growth and further iterations. 
