            .col-xs-12.col-md-6
                h5.caps PRODUCT ADOPTION
                p At RevUnit, we do not believe in the old adage, If you build it, they will come.  We do not believe in finishing a product and deploying it without a plan for success. This is why we fold Product Adoption into the process of every digital product we develop.
                p Product Adoption is the process of successfully onboarding new users and retaining   existing ones by engaging users throughout the product lifecycle.
                p Product Adoption does not only focus on the growth of a product or the retention of users, but instead it merges these two practices into one. We do this by employing Product Adoption Strategists from Day One of the build.
                p On the day of launch, marketing and communication plans are in place to grow the new product’s user base. Analytics are already installed to provide real-time data about the app’s success and real-time feedback to the product team. 
                p After launch, the Product Adoption Strategist continues to help market and grow the digital product by executing the adoption and retention plans and, based on user feedback, suggesting features or functionality to add.                       
