        .row.process-row
            .col-xs-12.col-md-6
                h5.caps ITERATION
                p As the digital product moves into the hands of users, built-in feedback and analytics tools measure the success of each product feature included in the MVP. Rather than using a predetermined road map, our team is prepared to continually improve the product with updates based on data gathered from actual users. 
                p Digital products built as MVP’s are intended to be iterated and improved upon. By design, they require product teams to be responsive to user feedback and then create new user stories to add to and improve the product. Through learning fast and iterating often, the well-researched MVP can quickly become a robust, yet focused digital product success.
